    <item>
      <title>据称 DSV 将在 Schenker 竞标中限制裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dsv-is-said-to-offer-to-limit-layoffs-in-schenker-bidding-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，DSV A/S 已承诺限制德国铁路物流部门的裁员人数，此举旨在使该部门的竞购战倾向于这家丹麦公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/dsv-is-said-to-offer-to-limit-layoffs-in-schenker-bidding-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行再次将利率降至 4.25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/bank-of-canada-cuts-rates-again-to-4-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行再次降息，并表示未来可能进一步降息。以行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆为首的政策制定者将基准隔夜利率下调至 4.25%。他表示，如果通胀继续放缓，预期进一步宽松是“合理的”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/bank-of-canada-cuts-rates-again-to-4-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
